    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, peel and finely slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> on a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 15 min, stirring occasionally, or until golden and caramelised</p><p>Once done, remove the pan from the heat and set aside for serving</p>",
