      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>honey</strong> with your <strong>mustard ketchup</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>honey mustard sauce</strong></p><p>Slice your<strong> apple[s]</strong> into matchsticks and discard the core[s]</p><p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>carrot[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>(no need to peel!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1624274492334-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1624274492334-x400.jpg",
