          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1624274492334-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1624274492334-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>apple matchsticks </strong>and <strong>grated carrot</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and <strong>mayo</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until fully combined – this is your <strong>apple & carrot slaw</strong></p><p>Remove the base of your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then wash under <strong>cold running water</strong> and cut away the core, then pat dry with kitchen paper </p><p>Tear the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> from the stem until you are left with a pile of leaves</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1624274497796-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1624274497796-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
