          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1624274497796-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausages have had 15 min, remove the tray from the oven and drizzle the <strong>honey mustard sauce</strong> all over them</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 10 min further or until the sausages are cooked through and the sauce is sticky – these are your <strong>sticky honey mustard sausages</strong></p><p>Tip: Turn the sausages a couple of times in the sauce to get them nicely coated!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1624274502807-x200.jpg",
