          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1624274508319-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill each<strong> mini ciabatta bun </strong>with a <strong>sticky honey mustard sausage</strong>, some of your <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>ketchup</strong> and the <strong>caramelised onions</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> sticky honey mustard posh dogs</strong> with the<strong> chips</strong>, <strong>apple & carrot slaw</strong> and<strong> torn lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Keep an eye out for it on the Everyday Favourites section of our menu.</span></strong></p>",
